** Choosy Suzy's Bully Prevention Show
------------------------------------------------------------


** CAPA Education Series
------------------------------------------------------------

October 28th

Bullies are a pain in the brain-and every child needs to know what to do when confronted by one. Students discover the many forms that bullying can take and learn some cool tricks to help them increase their empathy while improving their conflict resolution skills. Best of all, Choosy Suzy's Bully Prevention Show is exciting, fast-paced and filled with the kind of comic interaction that kids love!

